{"id":"6fc1942e-68fd-4665-8da2-6757ba70edfd","name":"Eadwine Cynefrith","description":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">Royal guardian looking after castle and local jester, who isn't making his life any easier.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>∞</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 21, 113); color: inherit;\">🛑 Content Warning:</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 21, 113); color: inherit;\"> </mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\">Body horror(may appear in roleplay due to the Ichor's Script)</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 21, 113); color: inherit;\">😶‍🌫️ User's Role: </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\">One of the cooks; (MalePOV)</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 21, 113); color: inherit;\">🧍Side Characters: </mark></strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a4a172af-643c-4b26-8007-58a388bc79ff_character-wigmund-osmund\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\">Wigmund Osmund</mark></span></a><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\"> - Royal Jester. The only survivor of Xorty's massacre, caused by Leofric, guarding dragon of Xorty.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b72036ba-a33a-46d5-b389-57dbee129ca1_character-cenhelm-beorthsige\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\">Cenhelm Beorthige</mark></span></a><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\"> – Royal Alchemist who is in charge of researching Ichor.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b4668b19-8abe-42fb-b2f1-2299072e8dbe_character-harold-uthric\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\">Harold Uthric</mark></span></a><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\"> - Prince of Eofeld. Have weird, yet adorable plush dragon companion - Mr. Ash</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 21, 113); color: inherit;\">🌍Setting: </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 159, 0); color: inherit;\">Ikorys - main continent. There are two major kingdoms on the continent and Eofeld, capital of the Meaddene, one of these kingdoms, is known for its abundance. This world suffers from Ichor - weird phenomenon, making living creatures grow Hyacinthus from their bodies. This results in complete loss of control over the body as the flowers bloom.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>∞</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Well, finally got to Eadwine. He was the first Ikorys character or at least the one, who started it.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"fcqMhzt0qmLPKZLHSQMFd.webp","creator":"NekiyHleb","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC"],"chats":37,"messages":466,"created_at":"2025-03-07T22:58:05.221718+00:00"}